247
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,720
We thought it was rather funny.

248
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,840
They really had this whole
attitude of,

249
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:31,920
"We cannot be seen to support
this kind of thing."

250
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:36,160
"This kind of thing" meaning
cross-dressing.

251
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:38,920
And it's funny -
it makes you laugh now,

252
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,880
but it made them drop the record.

253
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:47,040
The thing with America is
at the time, in the mid-'80s,

254
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:50,360
the way that people
had to be portrayed had to be so

255
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,600
cotton-candy clean.

256
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:57,760
You could not be seen to be gay
or you could not come out

257
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:00,880
during that period.
It was completely hidden.

258
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:04,120
# But life still goes on

259
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,480
I've heard people say to me,

260
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:07,680
"Oh, but Freddie denied he was
homosexual."

261
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:10,760
No, he didn't.
Look at the interviews. Look at it.

262
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:14,840
The NME asked him in about 1978.
They said, "Are you gay?"

263
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,840
And he said, "As a daffodil, dear!"

264
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:19,280
That is not a man
denying his sexuality.

265
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:22,680
But the funny thing is,
people didn't really hear it.

266
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,880
Freddie Mercury was a raving queen,

267
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:29,680
and he wouldn't mind
anybody saying it.

268
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:34,480
And it was quite amazing that most
people didn't even think

269
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:37,280
that Freddie Mercury was gay.

270
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:39,480
And then you look back
at the history of rock and roll,

271
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,920
and you look at Little Richard...

272
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:42,600
Let it all hang out!

273
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:46,120
With the beautiful Little Richard
from down in Macon, Georgia.

274
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:49,560
