453
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:29,320
with a sort of yeehaw fringe.

454
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:31,360
# My need is such

455
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:33,080
And it was just a laugh
with Freddie.

456
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:35,920
# I pretend too much

457
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,840
He said I've always fancied,
